### GET token-info - with optional X-Request-Id header
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/credentials/token-info
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9
X-Request-Id: req-12345

### GET token-info - without optional X-Request-Id header
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/credentials/token-info
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9

### GET token-info - missing required Authorization header (will fail)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/credentials/token-info
X-Request-Id: req-12345

### GET user-agent - required header
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/credentials/user-agent
User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36

### GET all headers - full headers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/credentials/headers
Accept-Language: en-US,en;q=0.9,es;q=0.8
Accept: application/json
X-Custom-Header: custom-value

### GET all headers - with default Accept value
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/credentials/headers
Accept-Language: es-ES

### GET all headers - without optional X-Custom-Header
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/credentials/headers
Accept-Language: fr-FR,fr;q=0.9
Accept: application/xml

### GET accepted - 202 Accepted with body
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/credentials/accepted

### GET no-content - 204 No Content (no body)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/credentials/no-content

### GET created - 201 Created with body
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/credentials/created